OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A mother who scrawled contact details  
OL,6, on her two-year-old daughter's back    
OL,7, while fleeing Ukraine has described to 
OL,8, the BBC her desperation in that moment.
OL,10,FSasha Makoviy said she wrote little    
OL,11,FVira's name, age and some phone numbers
OL,12,Fon her, in case the family were        
OL,13,Fseparated or killed while fleeing Kyiv.
OL,15,F"In case of our death, she could be    
OL,16,Ffound and would know who she is," Ms   
OL,17,FMakoviy explained.                     
OL,19,FThe family are now in France where they
OL,20,Ffeel "surrounded with love and care".  
